  "notes": "Executable local-runtime scenario for appUninstall error codes and cascade behavior. It avoids base-state seeding: the subscription, delegated token, and known-app-not-installed branch are earned through replayed proxy requests. The APP_NOT_FOUND and APP_NOT_INSTALLED message strings are Core-source-derived from components/apps/app/models/graph_api/admin/mutations/app_uninstall.rb:84-98 resolving I18n.t with scope apps.admin.graph_api_errors.app_uninstall and components/apps/config/locales/graphql/en.yml:37-38. Live billing/uninstall-capable Shopify capture remains blocked by the current custom-app Billing API limitation, so this spec does not claim fresh live billing parity for those messages."
